        Install
        ~~~~~~~
        
        github.com_: :code:`pip install git+git://github.com/russianidiot/write.py.git`
        
        pypi.python.org_: :code:`pip install write`
        
        download_: :code:`[ -e requirements.txt ] && pip install -r requirements.txt; python setup.py install`
        
        .. _github.com: http://github.com/russianidiot/write.py
        .. _pypi.python.org: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/write.py
        .. _download: https://github.com/russianidiot/write.py/archive/master.zip
        
        	
        
        	
        
        	
        
        Usage
        ~~~~~
        
        .. code-block:: python
        
        	from write import *
        
        	>>> write(path,'string')
        	>>> open(path).read()
        	'string'
        
        	>>> write(path,None) # touch
        	>>> open(path).read()
        	''
        
        	>>> write(path,42) # write integer
        	>>> open(path).read()
        	'42'
        
        	>>> write(path,dict()) # converted to str
        	>>> open(path).read()
        	'{}'
        
